  helpText: 'Welcome to the Fantasy Auto Battlefield!


    Here you will play cards
    summoning might creatures and buildings, conjuring ethereal effects in order
    to destroy the opponent''s base.


    The game consists of turns, each with
    5 phases:


    1. Upkeep: Here you will draw your turn card and gain mana


    2.
    Standard: Here the AI will play its cards and then you will be able to play yours


    3.
    Move: Now all units on the board will move one tile in front of them, if that
    tile is empty


    4. Combat: Now pawns that can target other pawns, will attack
    each other


    5. End: Now end turn effects happen (e.g terrain effects)'
